905
00:54:38,969 --> 00:54:40,231
in the middle of the night

906
00:54:40,337 --> 00:54:43,135
and away they went
without a word to me.

907
00:54:43,240 --> 00:54:48,234
Now this man with the
wooden leg, was he alone?

908
00:54:48,345 --> 00:54:51,007
Think he might have
had an animal with him.

909
00:54:51,114 --> 00:54:53,480
A dog?

910
00:54:53,583 --> 00:54:54,982
Didn't look like
no dog to me sir.

911
00:54:55,085 --> 00:54:57,849
More like something that
you find at the zoo.

912
00:54:59,356 --> 00:55:00,914
So tell me about
the launch.

913
00:55:01,024 --> 00:55:02,719
It's the old green bird
with the yellow line.

914
00:55:02,826 --> 00:55:03,986
Oh no, no, sir.

915
00:55:04,094 --> 00:55:05,254
The Aurora has just
been fresh painted

916
00:55:05,362 --> 00:55:06,761
black with a gold trim.

917
00:55:06,863 --> 00:55:09,024
Awe yes, with
a white funnel.

918
00:55:09,132 --> 00:55:11,430
No sir black funnel.

919
00:55:11,535 --> 00:55:13,127
Awe yes of course.

920
00:55:13,236 --> 00:55:14,396
Well thank you Mrs. Smith.

921
00:55:14,504 --> 00:55:15,471
Goodbye Jack.

922
00:55:15,572 --> 00:55:16,903
Bye.

923
00:55:24,581 --> 00:55:25,912
The main thing with
people of that sort

924
00:55:26,016 --> 00:55:27,483
is never to let them
think that information

925
00:55:27,584 --> 00:55:29,108
is of the slightest
importance to you.

926
00:55:29,219 --> 00:55:31,153
If you do they
will instantly

927
00:55:31,254 --> 00:55:35,190
shut up like an oyster.

928
00:55:35,292 --> 00:55:36,953
Well our course seems
pretty clear now.

929
00:55:37,060 --> 00:55:39,494
What would you do, then?

930
00:55:39,596 --> 00:55:40,995
Get on the track
of the Aurora.

931
00:55:41,098 --> 00:55:42,759
It would take days
if not months

932
00:55:42,866 --> 00:55:44,094
to search every wharf
and landing place

933
00:55:44,201 --> 00:55:45,793
on the harbor between
here and Greenwich.

934
00:55:45,902 --> 00:55:47,699
What do you propose?

935
00:55:47,804 --> 00:55:50,637
As our query has no
reason to fear that
he's being hunted

936
00:55:50,741 --> 00:55:52,800
I propose first
of all a bath.

937
00:55:52,909 --> 00:55:54,001
And shave.

938
00:55:54,111 --> 00:55:56,545
And then a good meal and
then some hours of sleep.

939
00:55:56,646 --> 00:55:58,409
At the same time

940
00:55:58,515 --> 00:56:00,574
mobilizing the Baker
Street division

941
00:56:00,684 --> 00:56:02,413
of the detective
police force.

