00:56:05,255 --> 00:56:08,088
In other words
the irregulars.

943
00:56:20,971 --> 00:56:23,371
Awe the energetic Jones
the ubiquitous reporter

944
00:56:23,473 --> 00:56:24,838
fixed up the case
between them.

945
00:56:24,941 --> 00:56:27,000
Watson look at this.

946
00:56:30,313 --> 00:56:31,746
Here.

947
00:56:36,553 --> 00:56:38,544
Mr. Jones' trained and
experienced faculties

948
00:56:38,655 --> 00:56:43,456
were at once directed
towards the detection
of the criminals.

949
00:56:43,560 --> 00:56:45,460
His well-known
technical knowledge

950
00:56:45,562 --> 00:56:48,998
and powers of
minute observation...

951
00:56:49,099 --> 00:56:50,999
well it gets better still

952
00:56:51,101 --> 00:56:53,228
the prompt and
energetic action

953
00:56:53,336 --> 00:56:54,496
of the officers of the law

954
00:56:54,604 --> 00:56:56,128
shows the great
advantage for the

955
00:56:56,239 --> 00:56:59,072
single vigorous
and masterful mind.

956
00:56:59,176 --> 00:57:01,576
Isn't it gorgeous?

957
00:57:01,678 --> 00:57:03,737
We had a close shave of
being arrested ourselves.

958
00:57:03,847 --> 00:57:05,371
I wouldn't answer
for our safety now

959
00:57:05,482 --> 00:57:07,109
if he has another of
his attacks of energy.

