00:57:35,312 --> 00:57:36,779
I've got your message.

967
00:57:36,880 --> 00:57:38,313
I brought 'em on sharp.

968
00:57:38,415 --> 00:57:42,249
3 bob and a tenner
for the tickets.

969
00:57:45,822 --> 00:57:48,290
Now Wiggins, in future

970
00:57:48,391 --> 00:57:50,291
they can report to
