the irregulars
will find her.

987
00:58:41,711 --> 00:58:44,771
They can go everywhere,
see everything.

988
00:58:48,318 --> 00:58:50,047
If our man had
an easy task

989
00:58:50,153 --> 00:58:52,417
just as ours ought to be.

990
00:58:52,522 --> 00:58:53,921
One-legged men
are not so common

991
00:58:54,024 --> 00:58:55,992
and this other man
must be unique.

992
00:58:58,128 --> 00:59:00,858
The aborigines of
the Andaman Islands

993
00:59:00,964 --> 00:59:02,693
may perhaps claim
the distinction

994
00:59:02,799 --> 00:59:06,394
of being the smallest
race upon this earth.

995
00:59:06,503 --> 00:59:08,232
They are a
fierce, morose,

996
00:59:08,338 --> 00:59:09,896
and intractable people,

997
00:59:10,006 --> 00:59:11,439
though capable of forming

998
00:59:11,541 --> 00:59:13,008
the most devoted
friendships

