00:59:13,109 --> 00:59:15,373
when their confidence
has once been gained.

1000
00:59:15,478 --> 00:59:20,245
They have always
been a terror to
shipwrecked crews,

1001
00:59:20,350 --> 00:59:23,786
braining the
survivors with their
stone-headed clubs

