1011
01:00:23,713 --> 01:00:25,271
You really must
get some rest.

1012
01:00:25,382 --> 01:00:26,679
I can't sleep.

1013
01:00:26,783 --> 01:00:29,183
This infernal problem
is consuming me.

1014
01:00:29,286 --> 01:00:31,083
No news?

1015
01:00:31,187 --> 01:00:32,017
None.

1016
01:00:32,122 --> 01:00:33,453
None whatsoever.

1017
01:00:33,556 --> 01:00:35,114
The whole river has been
searched from both sides.

1018
01:00:35,225 --> 01:00:36,658
Mrs. Smith has not
heard from her husband,

1019
01:00:36,760 --> 01:00:38,819
it's too much.

1020
01:00:38,928 --> 01:00:40,862
To be balked by
some petty obstacle

1021
01:00:40,964 --> 01:00:42,829
