been overcome.

1022
01:01:12,462 --> 01:01:14,692
See anything?

1023
01:01:14,798 --> 01:01:16,663
No nothing.

1024
01:01:46,463 --> 01:01:47,760
Shove off.

1025
01:01:47,864 --> 01:01:50,833
