1051
01:03:40,443 --> 01:03:42,343
Go to Baker
Street at once.

1052
01:03:42,445 --> 01:03:44,606
If I've not returned,
wait for me.

1053
01:03:44,714 --> 01:03:47,410
I am close on the track
of the Sholto gang.

1054
01:03:47,517 --> 01:03:48,677
Come with us tonight

1055
01:03:48,785 --> 01:03:50,047
if you want to be
in at the kill.

1056
01:03:50,153 --> 01:03:51,177
Good.

1057
01:03:51,287 --> 01:03:54,415
So he's on the
scent again?

1058
01:03:54,524 --> 01:03:57,322
He's been at
fault too has he?

1059
01:03:57,427 --> 01:04:00,760
